en_242038_0	Troops of both Indian Army and Sri Lankan Army, now on the verge of culminating their joint, 'Exercise-Mitra Shakthi' at Shivaneri demonstration village in Pune, India rehearsed final operational tasks with focus on general strategic planning.
en_242038_1	After the day's opening narratives and briefings were made and basic guidelines for the day's preparations were announced, both contingents started their actions and completed it before dusk.
en_242038_2	As part of a socialization segment, a birthday and a wedding anniversary of Sri Lanka and an Indian officer, engaged in the Exercise were celebrated upon completion of the day's routine.
en_242038_3	The Exercise is scheduled to end on 15 December 2019.
